latestPosts.caption:
We have made it till Lakmé Fashion Week ❤️🧿

I had this in my vision board of last summer, I knew this will come into reality some day and now when it has come, it’s EXACTLY HOW I PICTURED IT ❤️

Undoubtedly, there were hundreds of time I fell down and hundreds of time I chose to pick myself up, brush it off and keep going. 
Every fall taught me something new.
Made me consistent. Made me disciplined.
Made me ME! ✨

There were time where I didn’t show up, not being consistent with content, didn’t engage, didn’t interact still you guys made it through.

How did I get so lucky to have each one of you? 🤍

Honestly, BEYOND BEYOND GRATEFUL TO EVERY SINGLE ONE OF YOU! ❤️🧿

#lakmefashionweek #lakmé #nexaexperience #lakméfashionweek
